{"tid":2225632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"亞馬遜推掃描手掌付款","createTime":"2020-10-01T12:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T14:23:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"76e88cc3c2854bfcee1bc6c6ab5730e09c8e09fd","tid":2225632,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201001/H4EO66A6GVFY5LNCKO2JXJ2M5M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201001%2FH4EO66A6GVFY5LNCKO2JXJ2M5M%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w16d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=3fa3d890\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201001%2FH4EO66A6GVFY5LNCKO2JXJ2M5M%2F&h=600fdfa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201001/H4EO66A6GVFY5LNCKO2JXJ2M5M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜推掃描手掌付款<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eQbcMbUuk9Wg8Nuw3FaFqqU6M8I=/1145x886/filters:quality\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeQbcMbUuk9Wg8Nuw3FaFqqU6M8I%3D%2F1145x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w16d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=039c49bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeQbcMbUuk9Wg8Nuw3FaFqqU6M8I%3D%2F1145x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality&h=2d0c2409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eQbcMbUuk9Wg8Nuw3FaFqqU6M8I=/1145x886/filters:quality</a>(100)/<a href=\"http://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GOLWGFH4ZNBNBNZKG762BXMZLE.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGOLWGFH4ZNBNBNZKG762BXMZLE.jpg&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w16d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=6b3d9d23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GOLWGFH4ZNBNBNZKG762BXMZLE.jpg</a><br />\n■亞馬遜推出新支付系統，「出掌」便可付款。<br />\n<br />\n美國最大網上零售商亞馬遜前日推出新的支付模式「Amazon One」，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標榜快捷無接觸<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜形容系統「快捷、方便、無接觸」，消費者毋須成為會員，只要插入銀行卡，把支付選項與自己的手掌掃描連結；數據會被加密並儲存在雲端，消費者亦可上網刪除有關數據。亞馬遜指系統利用「專門設置的演算法和硬件」，掃描「皮膚表面和底下的特徵」。<br />\n<br />\n英國修咸頓大學電子及電腦科學學院博士哈拉克解釋，手掌辨識的原理是掃描手掌的靜脈排列，保安程度與指紋掃描相若，「每個人每隻手指的排列都不一，而且靜脈在皮膚底下，要偽造極困難」。<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜稱「正與數個潛在客戶商討」未來在其他店舖推出新系統，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過有關注私隱組織就批評亞馬遜把「入侵性的反烏托邦技術帶入市場，解決不存在的問題」，「沒有人應在消費時提供生物鑑定數據」。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/英國廣播公司"},{"pid":"032f30b4f3bb13ac8d99cab5d4d89af4ab17bf27","tid":2225632,"uid":46835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:51:56.000Z","msg":"我哋就仲喺度搞緊手掌量體溫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa3a80bc52c2b46d961931a274b10b7ce8f58f2","tid":2225632,"uid":66099,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:54:13.000Z","msg":"新surveillance tool<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8680ab61257591b3bcb3576d91891d3595ddf4","tid":2225632,"uid":13349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"我地偉大既袓國立法強制印QR code落手掌咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fdec21a3c6341139c9320d86e7feca1c3105a16","tid":2225632,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"凌空Scan？"},{"pid":"d5fbe21e272b8a3dc258b813649e85a927b30cf7","tid":2225632,"uid":205469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d8680ab61257591b3bcb3576d91891d3595ddf4","tid":2225632,"uid":13349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"我地偉大既袓國立法強制印QR code落手掌咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm